{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2526fe655b","title":"关于停止在深圳方面的演习准备打金门的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7fb0c4de4c","index":0,"year":1958,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"2526fe655b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"392e37ad10","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2526fe655b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中国人民解放军广州军区1958年8月13日关于在深圳方向上进行演习的部署给军委的报告上。"},{"id":"3d82e77d12","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2526fe655b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"德怀，即彭德怀，当时任中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长，主持军委日常工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"687b9c4cc9","type":"title","text":"关于停止在深圳方面的演习准备打金门的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2526fe655b"},{"id":"392e37ad10","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2526fe655b"},{"id":"3d82e77d12","type":"paragraph","text":"准备打金门，直接对蒋，间接对美，因此不要在广东深圳方面进行演习了，不要去惊动英国人","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2526fe655b"},{"id":"6805693d1b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2526fe655b"},{"id":"ed044c2a30","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十八日上午一时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2526fe655b"},{"id":"3f762811d2","type":"paragraph","text":"再：请叫空司注意：台湾方面可能出动大编队空军（例如几十架至百多架）向我反击，夺回金、马制空权。因此，我应迅即准备以大编队击败之。追击不要越过金、马线。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2526fe655b"}],"page":{"id":"66aad5bf45","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2526fe655b","start":70,"end":70}}}},"__N_SSG":true}